1. Proxy Pattern:
```
public interface Proxy {
  // This is the interface that the proxy will implement
}

public class ProxyImplementation implements Proxy {
  // This is the concrete implementation of the proxy
}

public class RealObject {
  // This is the object that the proxy is representing
}

public class Client {
  public void useProxy() {
    // This is the client code that uses the proxy
  }
}
